Core Agent Logic
1. JD Parser
Extracts skills, experience, role, and location
2. Matching Engine
Computes Match Score based on:
Skill overlap
Experience alignment
Availability
3. Outreach Agent (Key Innovation)

Simulates candidate responses:

Interest level
Notice period
Salary expectations
4. Scoring Engine

Match Score (0–100)
Interest Score (0–100)

Final Score = (0.6 × Match) + (0.4 × Interest)

Why This Scores High
Multi-factor scoring (not keyword-based)
Combines fit + intent (rare in ATS systems)
Explainable and transparent logic




